Create → Add new data 
Used to insert new records into the database. 
Example: Add a new student 
Name: Ravi 
Age: 21 
Read → View data 
Used to retrieve or display data from the database. 
Example: Show all students list 
In simple words: see stored information 
Update → Modify data 
Used to change existing data in the database. 
Example: Change Ravi’s age from 21 to 22 
In simple words: edit stored information 
Delete → Remove data 
Used to delete records from the database. 
Example: Remove Ravi from student list 
In simple words: remove stored information 
